- IDL for API
- language and platform neutral
- Provides client libraries automatically
- Optimised for interservice comms
- Serialize/Deserialize structured data

- Protofiles are converted to java class by plugin
- Protofile location: src/main/proto
- Install protocol buffer editor
- filename.proto

file content:
-------------
syntax="proto3";

option java_multiple_files=true;
option java_package="com.vinsguru.models";

message Person{
    string name=1;
    int32 age=2;
}

